{"tid":1129684,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【二手成交】淘大頂層特色戶呎價20868元 創屋苑史上新高","createTime":"2019-04-28T14:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T15:42:06.000Z","uid":43146,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"323c5eb311d3d7590b6252ff9328c79a5b600d3b","tid":1129684,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T14:48:30.000Z","msg":"利嘉閣地產鮑允中表示，九龍灣淘大花園M座頂層特色戶，實用242方呎，開放式間隔，另連天台，以505萬元成交，呎價20,868元，呎價破頂，創屋苑史上新高。這類型的單位只有3期才有，屬於罕有特色連天台單位，景觀開揚，最高3層高過對面4期，可遠眺飛鵝山上的屋群。是次呎價打破去年3月所造紀錄，為L座頂層5室，實用242方呎，另連天台，成交價498萬元，呎價20,579元。至於今次成交單位原業主在2011年以235萬元買入，持貨8年賺約270萬元或1.1倍。"},{"pid":"6d4c4550b418eb610675e624be12d5c6524a2e2a","tid":1129684,"uid":7814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T14:59:25.000Z","msg":"要天台都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新樓都算，呢d 咁撚舊嘅垃圾樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87c47d6ea4867497922423478a9d9f15a6cdc10","tid":1129684,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"淘大做咗大修未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a88e7c8825a6baed74f14eee73561b7bc2fc403","tid":1129684,"uid":198188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T15:42:06.000Z","msg":"淘大實升<br />\n對邊文化中心"}]}